Invocation Name: tongue twisters
des:
Ask Alexa for an interesting funtime with words and she will take you to these tongue twisting riddles . When using the skill, you can say "Alexa, next" to move to the next riddle. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill.
